5. Menu dan Fitur Platform
5.1 Struktur Menu Utama
5.1.1 Dashboard
•Overview Metrics: Total projects, active users, completion rate
•Recent Activities: Latest updates, pending approvals
•Quick Actions: New project, data import, report generation
•Alerts & Notifications: Critical values, deadline reminders
5.1.2 Project Management
•Project List: Filterable, sortable list dengan status indicators
•Project Details: Timeline, team members, budget tracking
•Task Management: Assignment, progress tracking, dependencies
•Document Repository: Version control, access permissions
5.1.3 Data Collection
•Field Data Entry: Forms untuk berbagai jenis survey
•Mobile Sync: Real-time atau queue-based synchronization
•Photo Documentation: Geo-tagged images dengan annotations
•Quality Control: Validation rules, approval workflows
5.2 Modul Spesialisasi
5.2.1 Modul Geoteknik
Subsurface Investigation:
•Borehole logging dengan standard templates
•SPT/CPT data entry dan visualization
•Laboratory test results management
•Cross-section generation otomatis
Analysis Tools:
•Soil classification otomatis (USCS, AASHTO)
•Bearing capacity calculations
•Settlement analysis
•Slope stability analysis
Reporting:
•Template-based report generation
•Auto-population dari database
•Customizable layouts
•Export ke PDF, Word, Excel
5.2.2 Modul Geofisika
Data Acquisition:
•Integration dengan geophysical instruments
•Real-time data streaming
•Quality control checks
•Data backup otomatis
Processing:
•2D/3D seismic processing
•GPR data analysis
•Electrical resistivity tomography
•Magnetic survey processing
Interpretation:
•Layer identification
•Anomaly detection
•3D modeling
•Integration dengan geological models
5.2.3 Modul Topografi
Survey Management:
•Control point management
•Traverse calculations
•Adjustment algorithms
