Platform GEOSYNC mengadopsi Scrum framework dengan sprint cycles 2 minggu:
Sprint Structure:
•Sprint Planning: 4 jam
•Daily Standups: 15 menit/hari
•Sprint Review: 2 jam
•Sprint Retrospective: 1 jam
Ceremonies:
•Backlog grooming mingguan
•Architecture review bulanan
•Security assessment quarterly
•Stakeholder demo setiap sprint
