•Error rate: Target < 0.1%
•Security incidents: Target 0
Business KPIs:
•User adoption rate: Target 80% within 6 months
•Customer satisfaction: Target NPS > 50
•Process efficiency: Target 40% improvement
•Cost reduction: Target 30% operational savings
8.3.2 Monitoring Framework
# Monitoring Configuration
monitoring:
  metrics:
    - system_health
    - user_activity
    - performance_indicators
    - business_metrics
  
  alerts:
    - critical_threshold: 99.5% uptime
    - warning_threshold: 2 second response
    - error_threshold: 0.5% error_rate
  
  reporting:
    - daily: system_health_report
    - weekly: performance_summary
    - monthly: business_review
    - quarterly: strategic_assessment
