8.5 Risk Management
8.5.1 Risk Assessment Matrix
Risk	Probability	Impact	Mitigation Strategy
Technical failure	Low	High	Redundant systems, backup plans
User resistance	Medium	Medium	Change management, training
Security breach	Low	Critical	Security audits, encryption
Budget overrun	Medium	High	Contingency planning, phased approach
8.5.2 Contingency Planning
