9.1 Ringkasan Rencana Pengembangan
Platform GEOSYNC represents a transformative leap in digital geotechnical practice, integrating cutting-edge technology with domain expertise to deliver unprecedented efficiency and accuracy. The comprehensive development plan outlined above ensures systematic progression from concept to full deployment, with careful attention to technical excellence, user experience, and business value.
9.2 Rekomendasi Strategis
Prioritized Actions:
1.Immediate commencement of Phase 1 development with focus on core functionality
2.Establishment of strategic partnerships with key technology providers
3.Development of robust change management program
4.Implementation of continuous monitoring and improvement framework
Success Factors:
•Strong executive sponsorship and governance
•User-centric design approach throughout development
•Agile methodology with regular stakeholder feedback
•Comprehensive training and support programs
9.3 Next Steps
1.Finalize budget approval and secure project funding
2.Assemble development team with required expertise
3.Establish project governance structure and processes
4.Initiate Phase 1 development with focus on MVP delivery
Platform GEOSYNC is poised to become the industry standard for digital geotechnical solutions in Indonesia, driving innovation and excellence in infrastructure development projects nationwide.

